Year = {2022},
Volume = {15},
Abstract = {We report, in this article, the process of compiling a corpus consisting
   of anime subtitles in Brazilian Por-tuguese, hereby named Anime
   Subtitles Corpus (CorLeAni). The corpus, currently with almost 1 million
   words, has been compiled following the theoretical-methodological
   support of Corpus-Based Translation Studies. The compilation took place
   over two Projects of Scientific Initiation of High School (PIBIC-EM),
   2019-2021 and 2020-2021, with a grant from the Instituto Federal
   Goiano-Campus Campos Belos. Recognizing that fansubs have great
   potential for discussions and studies in the audiovisual field, we have
   made CorLeAni available free of charge so it can be used in future
   linguistic and translation research.},
