   Engineering (ICCECE), Guangzhou, PEOPLES R CHINA, JAN 15-17, 2021},
Organization = {IEEE},
Abstract = {This paper presents two different methods to turn real people's photos
   into anime. The first method trains photo2cartoon codes with a totally
   different dataset. The second method divides cartoonization into three
   steps, which are: converting original image into line drawing, drawing
   color hints on line drawing, and finally colorizing. In order to train
   faster and take smaller spaces, a lighten method called LWAnimeGAN is
   developed. Our method is easy to implement and understand, and our goal
   is to save space and time for cartoonists.},
