   IEEE Comp Soc},
Abstract = {Anime line sketch colorization is to fill a variety of colors the anime
   sketch, to make it colorful and diverse. The coloring problem is not a
   new research direction in the field of deep learning technology. Because
   of coloring of the anime sketch does not have fixed color and we can't
   take texture or shadow as reference, so it is difficult to learn and
   have a certain standard to determine whether it is correct or not. After
   generative adversarial networks (GANs) was proposed, some used GANs to
   do coloring research, achieved some result, but the coloring effect is
   limited. This study proposes a method use deep residual network, and
   adding discriminator to network, that expect the color of colored images
   can consistent with the desired color by the user and can achieve good
   coloring results.},
