   a story creation system, Anime de Biog. Anime de Blog is an
   animation-based consumer-generated media (CCM) application. Users can
   create animated stories of affiliate advertising by simply inputting
   basic words using Anime de Blog. Through practical work experience of
   affiliate advertising on the Web by undergraduate students using Anime
   de Biog. students learned about an internet application, story
   marketing, and the concepts of affiliates and affiliate advertisements:
   they could also critically evaluate the application.},
